9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Wild Pear Tree | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Fresh out of university, a Turkish young man with literary aspirations returns to his home village and starts scraping together money to publish his book. While trying to reconnect with his old friends and environment; his uncertainty, existential struggle and his father’s gambling addiction bring him grave difficulties."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110988/the-wild-pear-tree"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Wild Pear Tree"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Fresh out of university, a Turkish young man with literary aspirations returns to his home village and starts scraping together money to publish his book. While trying to reconnect with his old friends and environment; his uncertainty, existential struggle and his father’s gambling addiction bring him grave difficulties."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/110988/the-wild-pear-tree"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s7kGE1MChkHD5VX8sv7SOGabGMZ.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Wild Pear Tree"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Fresh out of university, a Turkish young man with literary aspirations returns to his home village and starts scraping together money to publish his book. While trying to reconnect with his old friends and environment; his uncertainty, existential struggle and his father’s gambling addiction 